<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62abbac5-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2808"><num value="2808">§ 2808.</num><heading> Source of funds</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any expenses incurred by the Secretary under this chapter shall be paid from funds appropriated under <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s13">section 13 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62abbac6-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/379/s9">Pub. L. 101–379, § 9</ref>, <date date="1990-08-18">Aug. 18, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/477">104 Stat. 477</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
